## Version-bump policy

- **Patch bump (vN.M.P+1):** implementation refactor; no contract change; no determinism contract change. NOT recorded here.
- **Minor bump (vN.M+1):** input/output contract addition (additive); determinism contract preserved. Record above.
- **Major bump (vN+1.0):** breaking contract change; determinism contract may shift. Record above + party-mode consensus required.

